reviews.review_text:
We will survive.. This is excellent.
Strong Audience recording
of the boys in actual ‘meltdown’ country
Aka-Three Mile Island.
Always like Alabama as opener
Was getting to be a rarity
First set multiple peaks
Jam in Rooster!
Garcia sounds great on vocals
Weir punchy with Music
-) Don’t Ease= bonus tune

Touch- a rowdy version
❄️Estimated -) Eyes
(Somebody taping ❄️calls the Estimated)
Drums-)Space-heck yeah!
Imaginative set list
With great execution
This is why touring
Could be so much 🎆
(Hot show with a Day Job encore
I guess it was about
being grateful
for the whole trip)
beautiful  deliberate exit out of space
“We just keep Truckin’ on..”
More DEAD 🏴‍☠️
